{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"jQuery","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/jQuery","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>jQuery</strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\">ライブラリー</a> であり、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM</a> 操作を簡単にすること、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/AJAX\">AJAX</a> 呼び出し、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/event\">イベント</a> ハンドリングに注力しています。</span></p>\n\n<p>jQuery は <code>$(selector).action()</code> というフォーマットを使って要素をイベントに割り当てます。詳しく説明すると、<code>$(selector)</code> が jQuery を呼び出して <code>selector</code> 要素を選択し、&nbsp; <code>.action()</code>というイベント <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a> に割り当てます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ready</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>上のコードは下のコードと同じ関数を実行します:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>または</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"関連項目","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia の <a title=\"jQuery\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery Official Website</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technical_information","title":"技術情報","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://api.jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">API リファレンス文書</a><a href=\"https://api.jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"> </a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"関連項目","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"jQuery は JavaScript ライブラリー であり、DOM 操作を簡単にすること、AJAX 呼び出し、イベント ハンドリングに注力しています。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"jQuery","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/jquery","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/jquery/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/jQuery","title":"jQuery"}],"pageTitle":"jQuery - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}